e view you specify is a descendant of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class, you can use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view’s delegate to receive notifications when your control is tapped,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by implementing the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method. If the view you specify does not descend from ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", your view is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"responsible for handling any touch events within its bounds.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If this method is absent from the delegate, or if it returns ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout view has no accessory view on its right side. The return value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of this method is ignored if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" is present in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the delegate.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To display a view on the callout’s left side, implement the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:leftCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to modify the view that is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the right side of the standard callout bubble.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProje